body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:

J. Rea to Anna C. Johnson: Street, corner of 77th Street. Price, $14,750.
C. Larsen to Jessie Skinner: Parnell Avenue, corner of 121st Street.
J. Lister to John C. Johnsen: Bickerdike Street and Grand Avenue. Price, $1,600.
Pretzel to Olga Carlson: Christiana Avenue and Division Street. Price, $7,000.
M. Gunderson to Harry : Oak Park and North Avenues. Price, $6,200.
